            <title>[LUCENE-3268] TestScoredDocIDsUtils.testWithDeletions test failure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3268</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;ant test -Dtestcase=TestScoredDocIDsUtils -Dtestmethod=testWithDeletions -Dtests.seed=-2216133137948616963:2693740419732273624 -Dtests.multiplier=5&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In general, on both 3.x and trunk, if you run this test with -Dtests.iter=100 it tends to fail 2% of the time.&lt;/p&gt;
